{"tid":2302282,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚午 章魚肉飯咸強煲兒子飯 配 蒜茸鮮蝦春卷 響鈴鮮豆漿","createTime":"2020-11-27T04:03:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T07:32:14.000Z","uid":33359,"like":67,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"c63d66e29a9aaa63abc205ba50f28e1d3809d61f","tid":2302282,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T04:03:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iWC0c1i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiWC0c1i.jpg&h=a0650bf6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rWa86mp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrWa86mp.jpg&h=6f897d3b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FNcfMmu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFNcfMmu.jpg&h=6edb0210&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/URYZtzT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FURYZtzT.jpg&h=ef40e7ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然佢話就話係煲兒子飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n的確又見佢真係係個瓦煲倒出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係係完全無飯焦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n似係蒸飯多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過呢個價唔要求得咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n章魚肉餅好好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好濕潤<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n章魚味好香<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n肉餅都好軟熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蒜茸鮮蝦春卷係即炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拎到返公司仲熱仲脆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n餡料好新鮮飽滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我覺得蒜茸味有啲太搶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我落單個陣以為響鈴鮮豆漿係成碌響鈴插入豆漿到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇黎現實係響鈴牌既豆漿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n豆味唔太重<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無乜特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落個瞳孔好c伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69103721720cb4591409d700298af834c094211d","tid":2302282,"uid":3820,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T04:04:01.000Z","msg":"觀塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30c63e8b8fd6ef720421973c78e271d93f67c170","tid":2302282,"uid":364608,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T04:04:04.000Z","msg":"觀塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ed00a8125a20dda3718f7f4589aca7c2e5cbb5c","tid":2302282,"uid":129695,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T04:04:04.000Z","msg":"邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dd8ec776e90e711729155d3525f061fc7640c22","tid":2302282,"uid":184233,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T04:04:04.000Z","msg":"是靚午師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"791b2e81d71524452e82824a33461fefe446cfbf","tid":2302282,"uid":184233,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T04:04:17.000Z","msg":"觀塘師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be583a8e0616db36ae55cc3877fe890530826632","tid":2302282,"uid":5378,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T04:04:30.000Z","msg":"你依家收睇緊既是印度午廣告時段<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc0aaa5